⚙️ FINAL PIECE (AUTONOMOUS LOOP CODE – CORE IDEA)



Pseudo-core loop you’ll implement:



while (true) {

  const input = getUserInput();



  const shadowInsight = EVA_SHADOW.process(input, systemState);



  const decision = EVA_CORE.decide(input, shadowInsight);



  const tasks = EVA_CORE.decompose(decision);



  const results = executeTasks(tasks);



  EVA_SHADOW.learn(results);



  const summary = EVA_CORE.summarize(results);



  deliverToUser(summary);

}



